name: JAV Rina_石原○奈
description:
Rina is my favorite JAV actress of all time and I think her acting skills and performances during her time in the Attackers were the greatest in all of JAV history. It took me some time to finish this Lora because her images are really limited on the internet... But now here it is, though the result is not really satisfying, that is the best I can do for now, cheers.

I've updated my training method for better compatibility, and tuneability. It is now less overcooked compared to old ones.

If you want her to smile, just add "smile" to the prompt.

If you want a smile with teeth, just add "smile, teeth" to the prompt.

If you want a smile but a closed mouth, "smile, (closed mouth:1.5)" to the prompt and "teeth, open mouth" to the negative prompt.

I've also tested its tunability with hairstyles.

See all of these comparisons in the gallery.

For how I train LORAs, see description of JAV Anzai_RI○N | Stable Diffusion LORA | Civitai

Must turn on Hires.fix

Hires steps:17, denoising:0.5+

Use DPM++ 2M Karras or DPM++ SDE Karras

Strength: 0.5-0.9

She might look like someone from real life, but she is not what you think. She is a totally fictional character.

Checkpoint used for samples: Basil Mix, kanpiromix, majicMIX realistic and henmixreal

VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000 from StabilityAI

Legal & Risk

It is prohibited to use this model for commercial purposes and any scenarios of illegal acts and purposes.

本人原则上不支持使用此模型生成任何成人内容。用户在使用本模型时，请务必遵守当地法律法规，勿侵犯他人的名誉权、隐私权或肖像权。
